table.name: vessel
table.description: Stores vessels and information related to each vessel.

columns.name: VESSEL_GID
columns.description: Vessel Id

columns.name: VESSEL_NAME
columns.description: User specified name for the vessel; typically used if different from the GID

columns.name: OWNER
columns.description: Vessel owner

columns.name: OPERATOR
columns.description: vessel operator

columns.name: REGISTRY_PORT_LOC_GID
columns.description: vessel port of registry

columns.name: FLAG_COUNTRY_CODE_GID
columns.description: vessel country

columns.name: OFFICIAL_NUMBER
columns.description: official number for vessel

columns.name: CALL_SIGN
columns.description: vessel call sign

columns.name: IMO_NUMBER
columns.description: 7 digit number assigned to all ships

columns.name: CLASS_SOCIETY_NUMBER
columns.description: class society number for vessel

columns.name: YEAR_BUILT
columns.description: year vessel was built

columns.name: IS_IN_SERVICE
columns.description: Must be Y/N to indicate if vessel is in service.
